WEBVTT

00:00:00.618 --> 00:00:02.056
Ko sem se rodila jaz,

00:00:02.056 --> 00:00:03.736
je bila pravzaprav samo ena knjiga

00:00:03.736 --> 00:00:05.622
o vzgoji otrok

00:00:05.622 --> 00:00:08.789
in napisal jo je Dr. Spock.

00:00:08.789 --> 00:00:10.725
(Smeh)

00:00:10.725 --> 00:00:11.956
Hvala za tole.

00:00:11.956 --> 00:00:15.562
Vedno sem si želela to narediti.

00:00:15.562 --> 00:00:17.665
Ne, bil je Benjamin Spock,

00:00:17.665 --> 00:00:21.515
in imela je naslov
'Nega in vzgoja otroka'.

00:00:21.515 --> 00:00:27.162
Do njegove smrti se je prodala
v skoraj 50 milijonih izvodov.

00:00:27.162 --> 00:00:30.807
Danes, stopim kot mama šestletnika